message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR. This paper is about automatic question generation from text using neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE). Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper deals with generating questions that can be answered from a given text passage.
